## SQLite — Data Model

Schéma résumé (voir la version source): [docs/data-model.md](mdc:docs/data-model.md)

Tables clés:
- projects(id TEXT PRIMARY KEY, name TEXT, created_at TEXT)
- agents(id TEXT PRIMARY KEY, project_id TEXT, role TEXT, provider TEXT, model TEXT, allowed_tools_json TEXT, system_prompt TEXT, created_at TEXT)
- sessions(id TEXT PRIMARY KEY, project_id TEXT, agent_id TEXT, provider TEXT, provider_session_id TEXT, created_at TEXT)
- messages(id TEXT PRIMARY KEY, session_id TEXT, sender TEXT, content TEXT, broadcast_id TEXT, created_at TEXT)
- tasks(id TEXT PRIMARY KEY, project_id TEXT, title TEXT, status TEXT, assignee_agent_id TEXT, created_at TEXT)

Conventions:
- Timestamps ISO-8601 UTC
- Base locale: `./data/multi-agents.sqlite3`
- Indexes pour tri et recherches (voir doc)
